&gt;I think we should all focus at the research at hand and forget what everyone else is doing. I personally know Chris and think he&#39;s a great guy and frank feels the same way most days. This has gotten to the point where i can&#39;t even do a session anymore because i&#39;m so blocked by negative thoughts from this group it&#39;s pointless to concentrate on the box and get results. Honestly who cares what chris does anyway, does it really affect everyone&#39;s lives that much. I have a job and this is a hobby that i used to really like, but now this board has brought me down. It seems all people want to do is make this like a street fight with challenges and negative views and for what reason? If anyone is concerned about hearing Chris&#39;s audio, i have about 2 hours of box sessions from Eastern State on my web site for all to listen to. It&#39;s www.keyportparanormal.com and go to investigation and click on eastern state. All the audio is at the bottom of that page and you guys can judge for yourself and i heard a lot come out of that box that night personally because i repeated a lot of stuff back to chris that i heard. Enough already, let&#39;s move on to the next great thing. That radio shack hack was a great breakthrough here, let&#39;s just be happy we got that before it was shut down. Now we have another avenue to go down, but we can&#39;t do it with all these negatives out there. Let&#39;s move on to new topics and anyone out there that bought a Radio Shack box, start sharing your files with the group so it&#39;s not just us same 5 that post all the time.-Steve H.
